{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "asset_optimization", "user": "lindajones", "message": "Olivia, I'll need your assistance in reviewing the sustainability measures implemented in our asset management strategy.", "created_at": 1620500300000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "audit_team", "channel": "audit_updates", "user": "oliviamartinez", "message": "Sure thing, Linda. Let's schedule a meeting for next week. John, could you join us in discussing the audit procedures?", "created_at": 1620500400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "audit_team", "channel": "audit_updates", "user": "johnsmith", "message": "Absolutely, Olivia. I'll prepare some materials on our standard audit protocols and share them with you both before our meeting.", "created_at": 1620500500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "asset_optimization", "user": "lindajones", "message": "Thanks, John. Looking forward to it. Let's keep pushing towards our sustainability goals!", "created_at": 1620500600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "audit_team", "channel": "audit_updates", "user": "oliviamartinez", "message": "Team, as we wrap up the year, I wanted to share a summary of our 2024 audits. We completed utilization audits for 11 non-battery production assets across our North American facilities. Great job everyone!", "create_at": 1672440000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "audit_team", "channel": "audit_updates", "user": "johnsmith", "message": "Thanks for the update, Olivia. It was a productive year indeed. Looking forward to optimizing our asset utilization in 2025.", "create_at": 1672440600000}}
